E-commerce Fashion Store Landing Page — Luxury Beige
CATEGORY
E-commerce / Fashion Retail
DESIGN STYLE
Luxury editorial, warm alabaster palette, serif typography, grayscale images with slow color reveal, gold
accents
Overview
Build a luxury fashion landing page for ‘Maison Eclat, a high-end clothing brand. The palette is warm
alabaster (#F9F8F6) with charcoal (#1A1A1A) text and metallic gold (#D4AF37) used only as a hover
accent. All images default to grayscale and slowly reveal full color on hover (1500ms transition). The
layout uses intentional asymmetry — 7/5 column splits, offset content, bottom-left alignment. The
design should feel like browsing Chanel or Hermes online — serene, expensive, and deliberate.
Design Tokens

Background #F9F8F6 — Warm alabaster, like expensive paper

Foreground #1A1A1A — Rich charcoal, not pure black

Muted BG #EBESDE — Pale taupe for alt surfaces

Muted text #6C6863 — Warm grey for secondary copy

Accent #D4AF37 — Metallic gold, hover/focus only

Typography Playfair Display headers, Inter UI, italic serif placeholders

Radius Opx everywhere

Animations 500-2000ms, ease-out, cinematic

Page Sections
1. Navigation
~ Logo: MAISON ECLAT in small caps, wide tracking JetBrains Mono
~ Center nav: Women / Men / Collections / About in Inter medium, tur gold on hover (500ms)
~ Right: Search icon + Bag icon with item count — thin stroke lucide icons
~ Border-bottom: 1px #1A1A1A at 10% opacity
2. Hero — Split Asymmetric
~ 7-col image left / 5-col content right using CSS grid grid-cols-12
~ Left: Full-height portrait image (aspect 3/4), grayscale, no color reveal in hero (stays grey for editorial
effect), subtle inner border shadow
~ Right content aligned to bottom of the image using flexbox end
~ Overline: NEW COLLECTION" uppercase, 0.3em tracking, xs, gold
~ HL: "The Art of Wearing Nothing Extra’ — 72px Playfair Display, line-height 0.9, tight
~ Body: 18px Inter, warm grey, max-w-sm
~ CTA: ‘Explore Collection —' — underfine-only button that turns gold on hover
~ Framer Motion: image slides in from left (x-60 0), content from right, staggered
3. Featured Products

— 3-column grid. Each card: portrait image (grayscale — color on hover, 1500ms), product name in Playfair,
price in mono, "Add to Cart’ text link
— Hover state: image gains color, card bottom border tums gold, subtle shadow deepens
— Use CSS group hover: parent group, child grayscale-0 on group-hover
4. Brand Story — Dark Inverted Section
— Black background (¥1A1A1A), alabaster text
~ Two columns: Left large italic Playfair quote 48px / Right: body text + vertical decorative line on left of
paragraph
— Vertical text label ‘OUR STORY" rotated -30deg, positioned left edge — CSS writing-mode: vertical
~ Framer Motion: reveal via ciipPath from top as user scrolls
5. Lookbook — Masonry Grid
— CSS columns-3 masonry layout, gap-4
— 8 images of varying heights, all grayscale, color reveal on hover
~ Hovering one image dims others to 50% opacity — Framer Motion group interaction
6. Testimonials
— 3 cards horizontal, each with left gold border (4p) that appears on hover
— Avatar grayscale — color on card hover
— Star rating row scales up siightly on hover
~ Quote in Playfair italic, name in Inter smal, role in mono xs
7. Newsletter CTA
~ Centered, minimal: Join the Inner Circle’ h2, tagline, email input + submit
~ Input: bottom border only, italic serif placeholder
— Button: primary dark with gold siide-in from left on hover
8. Footer
~ 4 columns, thin top border, small sans-serif links, "MAISON ECLAT © 2025' in mono


